Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:08.75,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.75,0:00:10.38,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,thought uncle committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.13,0:00:14.57,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't such a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.57,0:00:18.24,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,He was a man that the more difficult things got, the more he'd bare with it and work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.16,0:00:21.75,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,And he never once complained about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:23.33,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:26.04,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,He even gave up sleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.04,0:00:27.92,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,and just focused on drawing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.84,0:00:32.76,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Moritaka, have you read "Kyojin no Hoshi?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.76,0:00:34.67,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:37.26,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Then you know Sakamoto Ryouma's line, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:38.89,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:41.14,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You really liked "Ashita no Joe," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.35,0:00:44.60,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.60,0:00:47.15,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, you don't need to say any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.15,0:00:49.73,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.73,0:00:50.37,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.52,0:00:54.55,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Azuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.87,0:00:56.98,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It's her mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.98,0:00:58.87,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,This is Azuki's mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:02.08,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Become great mangakas.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:05.33,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be here, rooting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:07.33,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.33,0:01:08.08,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.67,0:01:11.13,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I sure am blessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:13.26,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Not "I," "we!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.26,0:01:15.51,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what, I will make this dream a reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.97,0:01:17.43,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.59,0:01:20.39,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.97,0:01:22.47,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.14,0:01:24.10,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Starting tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.10,0:01:27.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, today, I'm going to start making my drawings into manga artwork!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:29.67,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,All right, and I'll take on making a name!
