Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:23.68,Main,Kawaguchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Most pros use G-pens.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:25.35,Main,Kawaguchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They let you control the strength of the lines...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:27.35,Main,Kawaguchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and brings out more atmosphere in the drawings.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:31.56,Main,Kawaguchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I couldn't master them, so I use a kabura pen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:31.56,TL Notes,Kawaguchi,0000,0000,0000,,TL note: The "kabura" in the pen name means "turnip," coming from the shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:35.48,Main,Kawaguchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I do gag manga so I can barely get away with it, but pros use G-pens.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:39.82,Main,Kawaguchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once in a while I try to use them, but they're really hard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:03:57.46,Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:04:00.51,Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:01.13,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:02.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:06.01,Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro, it's fine to work hard all night,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:08.33,Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,but if you fall asleep during the test then there's no point to it, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:10.16,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.03,0:04:13.81,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Finally done...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:17.18,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:20.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen someone fall asleep during a midterm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.66,0:04:22.61,Main,Suzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Saikou!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:26.04,Main,Suzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Did you study so hard it caused ya to doze off?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:27.39,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:30.70,Main,Kawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, the test's over, so you wanna catch a movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:32.80,Main,Suzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah! That sexy one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:34.39,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Sexy one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:36.64,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I've got stuff to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:38.86,Main,Kawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:41.83,Main,Kawasaki,0000,0000,0000,,He's been spending all his time with whatever that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:46.45,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,So were you up all night practicing drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:47.99,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I was at the workplace since midnight. {TLC}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:51.27,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,All the way until I got called by my parents to come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:56.11,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,In school, when I couldn't calm down, taking the test with this pen gave me momentum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:04:59.32,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Woah, you really did bring it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:02.40,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, if I can't get used to this, the whole thing's not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:04.53,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Manga doesn't have limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:05.20,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Limits?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:08.20,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like a test which has answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:11.16,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,There's no upper limit to drawings or stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:15.21,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,The better you can make them, the better off you are. {Check}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:16.17,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the workplace, you coming too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:17.29,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:18.83,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,You seem happy, Shuujin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:23.96,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Here, your duplicate key, Shuujin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:27.18,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can I really have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:30.10,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,It's more convenient for you to be able to go whenever you want, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:32.56,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:36.60,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,The test's over, so I can fully devote myself to this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:45.19,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! I knew your talent for drawing wasn't half bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.21,0:05:47.43,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,After just one day you're able to do manga quality drawings!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:49.37,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying those are totally no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:50.49,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,What about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:53.70,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,The lines are stiff and they're way too thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:55.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Those aren't drawings that can be used for manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:57.08,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:05:59.54,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I knew G-pens would be tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:02.92,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I can't draw the thickness of what I'm imagining in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.48,0:06:06.01,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It was giving me trouble, so I tried using a kabura pen, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:08.13,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Kabura pen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:09.18,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:12.43,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. When I hear of dip pens, I think of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:16.18,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle used these when he couldn't figure out how to use G-pens either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:21.36,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,He was told to use G-pens by his editor,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:24.28,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,but because of its odd tendencies he couldn't master it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:26.44,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,so he just used the kabura pens.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:33.33,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to get different line strengths, but its easier to draw lines at a fixed thickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:38.29,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,G-pens let you control the strength of the lines, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:42.50,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,it's easy for them to get caught on the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:44.55,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:47.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So even though your uncle became a pro using a kabura pen,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:48.84,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,that's no good for us, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:52.89,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! It can't give the drawings flavor or atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:56.43,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle shrugged it off, saying "my drawings are crappy."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:58.81,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,And since he was doing gag manga, he said he could get away with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:00.35,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.16,0:07:06.05,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, it's totally different from doing rough sketches with a pencil or doing watercolor painting with a brush.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.67,0:07:08.38,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I've got no choice but to keep drawing until I get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.30,0:07:11.79,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I drew these yesterday, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:16.16,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These are good! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:17.83,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I better not say so.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:20.50,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saikou's still not satisfied with them{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:24.25,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Kabura pens are good for drawing backgrounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:28.46,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,And round pens are good for extra-thin lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:32.89,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,So you drew by looking at those?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:33.46,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:36.72,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I got them all out of the boxes and lined them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:39.56,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,So they sell this kind of sample material?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:42.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,With these you'll be able to draw manuscripts perfectly, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:44.06,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I need to put effects in, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:45.44,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Effects?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:47.98,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,These.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:51.82,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle directed his assistants on which to use with numbers,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:53.70,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,but first I have to be able to do them myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:56.45,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,All these kinds of lines can be drawn by hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:58.66,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,While using these sorts of rulers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:02.58,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any assistants,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:04.99,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,so I even have to put in the screen tones myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.07,0:08:08.37,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I used a cutter to cut these out and put them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:13.26,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,So in short, in order to make one page of a manuscript...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:18.56,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,First you start with a name and make it an under-sketch on a paper used for manuscripts...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:20.43,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Then you ink the characters and backgrounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.97,0:08:26.23,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. And then you ink in the effects and affix the screen tones...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:28.19,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,And then it's finally finished, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:31.38,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,There sure is a lot to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:31.99,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:37.57,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,The exact operation may vary depending on the person, but
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:42.29,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's got this feeling in general.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:46.14,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,When I realized how much I have to master before I can draw something we can bring in, I got impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.86,0:08:49.12,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Still humans are easy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:53.56,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,but movement, facial expressions, composition...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:55.72,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Unless I can draw them all, I'll never be a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:58.01,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how long it's gonna take...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:04.93,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking about it now, it's amazing that Uncle only took three years to go from a total beginner to his debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:07.86,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,And he didn't even know about the existence of white-out,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:11.56,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,so if he made even a little mistake, he'd have to redo that whole page.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:14.05,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,H-Heh, is that right...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.05,0:09:15.50,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,But we've gotta do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:17.95,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,An anime adaptation by 18...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:20.31,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I really can't waste even a single second!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:22.18,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Saikou,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:28.27,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel but I think you should at least study on days before tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:29.73,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:34.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I planned to study a little yesterday, but it was morning before I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.58,0:09:35.76,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,"Before you knew it..."?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:38.86,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, right now I just need to put in effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.86,0:09:40.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle used to say that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.38,0:09:42.87,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,It was one of his requirements for becoming a mangaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:44.49,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Requirements for becoming a mangaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.09,0:09:47.20,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,For the "Kawaguchi Tarou type."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:49.52,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Three major requirements for if you're not a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:52.90,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tell me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:56.86,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,First: hubris. {This is also written on screen. "The first" is small. "Hubris" is big.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:10:07.33,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H344546&\fnOlivia Brush\fs56\pos(100,100)}First
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:10:07.33,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H344546&\fs72\b1\fnOlivia Brush\pos(185,180)}HUBRIS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.38,0:09:59.99,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Think you're better than everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:01.91,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I've got that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:05.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But then it's not so much hubris, I have actual talent...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:07.33,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,That's what hubris is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:10.38,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Second: effort. {Same thing here. Written onscreen is "The second" small and "effort" big.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:14.13,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H1F2526&\fnOlivia Brush\fs56\pos(100,100)}Second
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:14.13,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs72\b1\fnOlivia Brush\c&H1F2526&\fsp-2\pos(185,180)}EFFORT
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:14.17,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,So he can be straightforward, too, that Kawaguchi Tarou-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:15.76,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,And last:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:16.88,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Yup?
