Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:49.89,TS,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs75\3c&H94B7B1&\c&H323E3C&\b1\fnMyriad Pro\fscx110\fscy120\fsp-1\move(744,280.5,744,285)\frz359.604\bord3\be8} Niizuma Eiji (15) Aomori
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:49.93,TS,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs75\3c&H94B7B1&\c&H323E3C&\b1\fnMyriad Pro\fscx110\fscy120\fsp-1\move(744,285,744,288)\frz359.604\bord3\be8\bord3\be8} Niizuma Eiji (15) Aomori
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:12:00.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fifteen years old?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:08.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fifteen years old?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.63,0:12:11.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It says here he's a high school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.32,0:12:13.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Received high praise from all the judges.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:15.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Niizuma Eiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.37,0:12:17.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is kind of annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:19.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,His acceptance speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:22.33,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Even when everyone was playing video games and hanging out,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.33,0:12:25.17,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I found it worthwhile to work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:28.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I am looking forward to continuing that work and contributing energetically to the pages of Jack Magazine."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:32.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like he's taking a jab at me, since all I did was play video games up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.51,0:12:36.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take us no time at all to surpass this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.89,0:12:40.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you look closely, you'll see that the only thing he's being praised for is his art.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:41.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's some confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:44.83,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Confidence, effort and luck are all that count.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:47.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,More like hubris, effort and luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.86,0:12:49.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think "confidence" sounds better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.65,0:12:52.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, check out the new "Kochikame."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:56.26,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,15 years old and he's a semi-finalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:12:59.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Moritaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.24,0:13:02.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand you're happy about getting that key,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.89,0:13:05.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but do you have to spend every day hanging around your uncle's studio?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:07.82,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You have exams to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.82,0:13:08.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.96,0:13:10.72,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:12.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, then start studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.03,0:13:14.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I get seconds please?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.99,0:13:15.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:18.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kayoko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:26.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading up to the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:30.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up, I'm coming too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.63,0:13:34.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome, it's totally {\i1}moe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.53,0:13:37.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like, you're gonna be a pro mangaka in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.49,0:13:41.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well you know, if I really get serious I might just change the industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:42.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:45.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come up with the story this time, so you can just focus on the art.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.94,0:13:49.18,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't mind, but I have high standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:53.92,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can I ask you a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:54.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.44,0:13:57.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they all looking in the same direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:14:00.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And you've only drawn them to the shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:05.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys were laughing at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.98,0:14:07.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Takagi from Class 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:09.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was the other guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:11.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not sure, what was his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.19,0:14:13.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.71,0:14:14.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyoshi Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.11,0:14:17.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Azuki's best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.05,0:14:18.11,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:19.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was talking about the guy doing the drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.95,0:14:23.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishizawa, he was in my class during second year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.83,0:14:25.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he also trying to become a mangaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:26.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:30.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he's just telling people he's drawing manga in order to attract attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.88,0:14:34.92,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyoshi was making fun of him, so I don't think he'll get too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.09,0:14:41.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't start slacking off just because midterms are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.84,0:14:44.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your real test is going to be the high school entrance examination.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.99,0:14:49.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please use these midterms as a base to think seriously about your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:51.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:53.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, then I'll begin the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.18,0:14:57.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I was able to polish up the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.78,0:15:00.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get to the studio and work our asses off writing names!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:03.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Saikou?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:04.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:08.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there are a lot of guys like us trying to become mangaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:13.43,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\fnImpact\bord3\shad2\move(403,-30,403,92)\3c&H2C4951&\c&H4632D9&}SUMMER TRAINING COURSE\N{\c&HF0FAFD&\fs27}This {\c&H4632D9&}Summer is {\c&H16C3CD&}Your Chance{\c&HF0FAFD&\i1}!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:13.43,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\fnImpact\shad2\bord3\an1\move(460,702,460,830)\4c&H1F2E37&\3c&H1F2E37&}{\c&H4632D9&}Get Ahead{\c&HF2FBFD&} by\N{\c&H16C3CD&}Improving\N\h\hYour Basic Skills{\i1\c&HF2FBFD&}!!{\i0}\N-{\c&HA99A63&}North{\c&HF2FBFD&} Shirokita Prep
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.10,0:15:10.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.10,0:15:13.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy, "Niizuma Eiji", was only 15, and there's Ishizawa..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.95,0:15:16.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know where he's going.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:20.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind going to North Yakusa High.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:25.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,North Yakusa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.78,0:15:29.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be easy for a top-scorer like you, Shuujin,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.74,0:15:32.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but this is the lowest level my dad will accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:35.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to set aside some time to just draw manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:38.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,All in order to become a mangaka, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:42.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never thought of my time as being so precious before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.31,0:15:45.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never gotten this much into anything before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:49.76,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But Saikou, are you sure you're okay going to a different high school from Azuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:51.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where she's going.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.46,0:15:53.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,She might even wind up at an all-girls school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:54.17,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask her then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.53,0:15:56.66,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll go to a different school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.66,0:15:59.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be more... romantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.09,0:16:01.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.03,0:16:03.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The DNA of a romanticist!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:07.15,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\blur.6\fnOlivia Brush\b1\bord0\move(1050,288,1114,288)\c&H81708C&\frz348.832}GRADUATION
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:07.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The next time we meet after graduating from middle school,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:07.23,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.6\fnOlivia Brush\b1\bord0\pos(1114,288)\c&H81708C&\frz348.832\clip(m 1137 426 l 1118 266 1133 113 945 238)\t($start,$end,\clip(m 955 378 l 945 268 937 95 786 202))}GRADUATION
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.56,0:16:11.76,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)}will be when I am a mangaka, and Azuki is a seiyuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:16.32,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)\fnTahoma\bord0\fscx110\frz17.278\pos(600,352)\blur0.5\c&HB1B2B6&}Do your best
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.01,0:16:15.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}Until then, we'll just encourage one another through mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.88,0:16:18.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:18.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:23.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you don't have to try so hard to imitate your uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:24.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:27.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's what Azuki wants too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:32.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Saikou, are you even thinking about the possibility that Azuki might get a boyfriend in high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:34.43,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:36.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I trust her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.88,0:16:40.76,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to North High, even if it means being apart from Azuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:43.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to have more time to write manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:44.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.67,0:16:50.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go to North High too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:51.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:54.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You should go to prep school!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:56.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're seriously trying to become mangaka,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:17:00.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,it would be more convenient and time efficient for us to be in the same school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.46,0:17:03.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel the same way you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:07.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I was really happy to get this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.93,0:17:09.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to try to get into a good university,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:11.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,, in case this mangaka thing didn't work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:14.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But it wouldn't be right to assign priority to a contingency plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:15.83,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuujin?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:17.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So North High, it's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.88,0:17:19.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't flunk the test, Saikou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:22.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, no problem, then we can focus on manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.22,0:17:26.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't keep letting our peers beat us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:28.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:31.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So our current rival is Niizuma Eiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.87,0:17:34.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard something about Eiji getting assigned an editor...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.10,0:17:38.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and being serialized at the time of his graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:40.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He already has an editor?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.48,0:17:43.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He definitely got one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:45.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He got one automatically when he won the prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:49.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he hadn't won, he could have just found an editor he was on good terms with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:51.83,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what my uncle was saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.83,0:17:53.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,An editor, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.42,0:17:56.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Eiji is getting ahead of us by leaps and bounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:17:59.33,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And there are good and bad editors too,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:02.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,so it doesn't seem like it'll be as simple as just {\i1}getting{\i0} one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.25,0:18:04.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not in our power to choose though,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.53,0:18:06.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,so whether or not we can find a good one...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.01,0:18:07.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Luck, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:11.11,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are editors who do nothing but spew misguided criticism,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:16.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,or who just slack off after picking up the manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:17.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.12,0:18:21.72,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you a story I found a bit moving, about an editor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.30,0:18:28.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He told a newcomer that had some work published in another magazine "your work has promise,"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:32.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,"so write as much as you can and bring it here," and kept putting pressure on him to write more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:37.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But when he finished reading through the tenth manuscript the newcomer brought him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.10,0:18:40.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He fed it through a shredder?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:44.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you find that moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.30,0:18:49.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That newcomer was always getting rejected after only having the first few pages of his manuscript read.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.83,0:18:53.11,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, he was happy that the editor had read his work to the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:58.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and he used the frustration of seeing his work shredded as a spring, and proceeded to become a popular artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:01.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it becomes a good story from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:03.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, at the meeting to discuss his serialization,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:05.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm sorry about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:09.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I thought that you would grow more if I didn't praise you."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:11.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Thank you so much."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.90,0:19:15.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:19.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That editor went on to become editor-in-chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.91,0:19:22.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like a manga plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.23,0:19:28.92,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,My uncle said most editors out there are just as passionate about manga as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:32.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That they all love manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.58,0:19:34.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.62,0:19:35.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:37.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna go meet an editor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:43.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If we call 'em up and tell him we want to show him a manuscript, we could meet one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:46.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Meet, but- We don't have a manuscript to bring yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.89,0:19:49.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's finish one up by the end of summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.51,0:19:53.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll bring it to "Jack."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:57.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're looking to get it serialized and turned into an anime,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.14,0:19:58.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Jack" is our best bet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:01.06,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If we get rejected then we'll be no worse off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.06,0:20:05.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see how they react after seeing our manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.84,0:20:09.18,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see how far our current skills can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.41,0:20:11.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:15.83,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll complete our work during summer break,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.83,0:20:17.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and bring it to "Jack!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.39,0:20:20.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's decided, then let's get to the studio!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:21.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:26.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.36,0:20:34.41,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Azuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.22,0:20:37.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard she had a little sister in 5th grade,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:39.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but her sister's cute too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:41.82,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:43.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's bad about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:44.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your chance to ask her for her email.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.63,0:20:48.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's with that powerful mother of hers. {qc - powerful?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:49.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you ask her if it was one on one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:51.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:55.90,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just pass by and pretend we didn't notice them, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:57.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd notice her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:20:58.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:03.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Azuki noticed us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:07.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's clearly blushing, and she's moved behind her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.46,0:21:09.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need you to report.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.79,0:21:23.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Miho, aren't those your friends from class?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:26.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Sis, you're blushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.59,0:21:27.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mina!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:31.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you and Azuki are shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:34.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you can feign indifference when you're in the same classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.19,0:21:35.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I said shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.91,0:22:33.70,TS,static,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\blur6\bord0\pos(296,508)\c&H0A191C&\shad0}Niizuma
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.61,0:22:34.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The editor-in-chief is also showering you with praises for your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.70,0:22:34.83,TS,focus,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\shad0\blur6\bord0\t(0,500,\blur0\fscx102\fscy102\shad1)\c&H0A191C&\move(296,508,296,510)}Niizuma
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.17,0:22:38.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I also think you have great talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.81,0:22:41.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we were wondering if you would be willing to come to Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.70,0:22:44.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Niizuma-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.72,0:24:20.06,TS,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\b1\c&HE6E7E5&\pos(1064,254)}Preview of \NNext Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.01,0:24:17.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't Takagi-san like you, Miho?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.96,0:24:18.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.44,0:24:20.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, wasn't he asking you about your dreams before?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.75,0:24:21.43,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.43,0:24:22.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.21,0:24:23.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll tell you later. {lit. "Maybe you'll understand sooner or later" but I thought this sounded better}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.32,0:24:24.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Maybe?!"
