Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.30,0:24:26.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Summer and Name"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.10,0:24:28.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A busy dream-filled summer!
